hwMeta.bodyText:
If(clk._onRisingEdge(),
    If(rst_n._eq(0),
        write_ptr(0),
        read_ptr0(0),
        looped0(0)
    ).Else(
        write_ptr(write_ptr_next),
        read_ptr0(read_ptr0_next),
        looped0(looped0_next)
    )
)

If((dataIn_0_vld & isSelected_0)._eq(1),
    dataOut_id(dataIn_0_id),
    dataOut_addr(dataIn_0_addr),
    dataOut_len(dataIn_0_len),
    dataOut_rem(dataIn_0_rem)
).Elif((dataIn_1_vld & isSelected_1)._eq(1),
    dataOut_id(dataIn_1_id),
    dataOut_addr(dataIn_1_addr),
    dataOut_len(dataIn_1_len),
    dataOut_rem(dataIn_1_rem)
).Else(
    dataOut_id(None),
    dataOut_addr(None),
    dataOut_len(None),
    dataOut_rem(None)
)
